3. Sequence Diagram: Park Vehicle
User
 |
 | 1. POST /parking/park (Vehicle)
 v
ParkingController
 |
 | 2. service.park(vehicle)
 v
ParkingService
 |
 | 3. strategy.findSpot(floors, vehicle.type)
 v
ParkingStrategy
 |
 | 4. (finds available spot)
 v
ParkingService
 |
 | 5. spot.park(vehicle)
 v
ParkingSpot
 |
 | 6. (marks spot as occupied)
 v
ParkingService
 |
 | 7. return ticket
 v
ParkingController
 |
 | 8. return ticket to user
 v
User
